"<c f0df60>You can set up your team, view members' history with the team, or disband the team. (Team leaders only)<c>"

"You have been scouted by $(1) on the team $(0).

The scouting request may have already been canceled."

"チーム「$(0)」の
$(1)からチームへの
スカウトを受けました。

"Team [$(0)] proposed to
absorb Team [$(1)].

*Appointments of all members who joined
Team [$(1)] will become Visitors.

*All ongoing receiving orders of all members in
Team [$(1)] will be destroyed.

*The team points ($(4)) possessed by
Team [$(2)] will be added to
that of Team [$(3)].
If the points reached above 99,999,999, they will
be truncated. (All other data will be deleted.)

Do you agree to the application to merge the teams? "

"By accepting the proposed merger from
$(1) of Team[$(0)] ,
you will become part of the team.
*Team [$(2)] will be deleted.

Is this ok?"

"Team [$(0)] proposed to
merge [$(1)] to their team.
Do you want to open the Reply Window?

*If there are items deposited in the warehouse of
team [$(1)], merger will not be possible."

"Do you want to propose [$(0)]
to be merged to [$(1)]?"

"Merger of teams have been proposed.
Awaiting reply from the other team..."

"Merger proposed from
$(1) of Team[$(0)]
will be rejected.
Is this ok?"

"Merger is not possible as the number of total members
after the merger has exceeded the fixed limit.
Please confirm the conditions of both individual teams."
"As the team merger has been turned down, merger cannot begin."

"As there are items in the warehouse of team
[$(0)], merger is not possible."
"Application of merging teams was turned down."
"Application of team merger of $(0) was rejected."

"Team [$(0)] was merged to
Team [$(1)].

*Appointments of all members who joined
Team [$(2)] have become Visitors.

*The team points ($(4)) possessed by
Team [$(2)] were added to
that of Team [$(3)].
(All other information were destroyed.)"
